<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. ءِ وَطُولَ جَفْوَتِهَا مِنْ الْهِجْرَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هَلْ فِيكَ مُعْتَبَرٌ فَيَسْأَلُوا عَاشِقٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بِمَصَارِعِ الْعُشَّاقِ كُلَّ زَمَانِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَكِنْ عَلَى تِلْكَ الْعُيُونِ غِشَاوَةٌ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَعَلَى الْقُلُوبِ أَكِنَّةُ النِّسْيَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَأَخُو الْبَصَائِرِ حَاضِرٌ مُتَيَقِّظُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مُتَفَرِّدٌ عَنْ زُمْرَةِ الْعُمْيَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَسْمُوا إِلَى ذَلِكَ الرَّفِيقِ الأَرْفَعِ اَلأَ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>عْلَى وَخَلَّى اللِّعْبَ لِلصِّبْيَانِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَالنَّاسُ كُلُّهُمْ فَصِبْيَانٌ وَإِنْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>بَلَغُوا سِوَى الأَفْرَادِ وَالْوِحْدَانِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَإِذَا رَأَى مَا يَشْتَهِيهُ يَقُولُ مَوْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>عِدُكِ الْجِنَانُ وَجَدَّ فِي الأَثْمَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَإِذَا أَبَتْ إِلا الْجِمَاحَ أَعَاضَهَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>بِالْعِلْمِ بَعْدَ حَقَائِقِ الإِيمَانِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَيَرَى مِن الْخُسْرَانِ بَيْعَ الدَّائِمِ الْـ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>بَاقِي بِهِ يَا ذِلَّةَ الْخُسْرَانِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَيَرَى مَصَارِعَ أَهْلِهَا مِنْ حَوْلِهِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَقُلُوبُهُمْ كَمَرَاجِلِ النِّيرَانِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>حَسَرَاتُهَا هُنَّ الْوُقُودُ فَإِنْ خَبَتْ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>زَادَتْ سَعِيرًا بِالْوُقُودِ الثَّانِي<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>جَاؤُا فُرَادَى مِثْلَ مَا خُلِّقُوا بِلا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>